ited-timestamp title=\"Monday, August 4, 2025 4:46 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1404304248983781567", "author": "CMDR Zzzz", "author_handle": "cmdrzzzz", "user_id": "329550145748336640", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/329550145748336640/469595727347b114f7981c86346cfb3c.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, August 10, 2025 11:23 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-10 11:23 p.m.", "text": "Following!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Following!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1404304597962461268", "author": "dickovich (VK6HOG)", "author_handle": "dickovich", "user_id": "1006911591276621946", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1006911591276621946/91720879d0d560f1dbbae20344f84610.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, August 10, 2025 11:25 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-10 11:25 p.m.", "text": "Another three repeaters have been made just waiting to find suitable locations !", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Another three repeaters have been made just waiting to find suitable locations !</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1404305394712444969", "author": "CMDR Zzzz", "author_handle": "cmdrzzzz", "user_id": "329550145748336640", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/329550145748336640/469595727347b114f7981c86346cfb3c.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, August 10, 2025 11:28 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-10 11:28 p.m.", "text": "Nice! I'm digging out some mounting hardware for the roof of my house to see if I can get a better line of sight and add to the mesh in some way, maybe I'll run a repeater as well if it's needed.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Nice! I&#39;m digging out some mounting hardware for the roof of my house to see if I can get a better line of sight and add to the mesh in some way, maybe I&#39;ll run a repeater as well if it&#39;s needed.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1404390459861630996", "author": "dickovich (VK6HOG)", "author_handle": "dickovich", "user_id": "1006911591276621946", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1006911591276621946/91720879d0d560f1dbbae20344f84610.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, August 11, 2025 5:06 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-11 5:06 a.m.", "text": "Meshcore relies on repeaters ! It’s very different to Meshtastic where the nodes fwd on and they discourage lots of repeaters, in core they don’t so growing a repeater network is important ! I’m in Belmont, have one on the hill in Goosberry Hill, one soon in Mt Pleasant - are you anywhere high ? Please setup a repeater ! (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Meshcore relies on repeaters ! It’s very different to Meshtastic where the nodes fwd on and they discourage lots of repeaters, in core they don’t so growing a repeater network is important ! I’m in Belmont, have one on the hill in Goosberry Hill, one soon in Mt Pleasant - are you anywhere high ? Please setup a repeater !</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Monday, August 11, 2025 5:06 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_h